I won’t do furry stuff, NSFW stuff (minor gore is fine) or super detailed robots/machines. I will do animals, but know I’m not the best at them and that my specialty is humanoid stuff.

My email is etheartist2603@gmail.com. My paypal is the same.

Sharing is highly appreciated!
